<Layout title="Nardelli" currentPath={Astro.url.pathname}>
	<h1>Welcome</h1>

	<p>
		Welcome to <strong>Nardelli Nespolo</strong>, a homely escape on the Tuscan–Umbrian border. We hope you enjoy everything Umbria and Tuscany have to offer — and that the house makes a perfect base for exploring the area at your own pace.
		We want everyone who stays at Nardelli to have a wonderful experience and to fall in love with this corner of Italy the way we have.<br><br>
		Nardelli was built by <strong>Billy McCarthy</strong> back in <strong>19XX</strong>, and it became a place that Billy and his partner <strong>Des</strong> truly cherished. They shared it generously with friends and family, and guests were always welcomed with open arms.
		Billy passed away in <strong>2016</strong>, but the house was left to the wider family to continue enjoying and sharing. We’ve all grown very fond of Nardelli and the surrounding area — and we hope you will too.
	</p>
<p style="margin-top: -6px; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 600;">
	
	Everything you need for a relaxed stay at Nardelli — from house basics to local favourites.
</p>

<p>
	We created this website to help you settle into Nardelli and get acquainted with everything it has to offer. It covers the essentials about the house and the local area, along with our recommendations for nearby restaurants, bars and day trips. And when it’s time to say goodbye, please don’t forget to use the <strong>Leaving Checklist</strong> before you go.
</p>
	
</Layout>